Profitap | Full-Stack Developer | Eindhoven, The Netherlands | Onsite, Fulltime | www.profitap.com

Our hardware and software engineers develop cutting edge network monitoring equipment and network analysis software. We are looking for an experienced Full-Stack Developer that will support our team of engineers in creating the best network monitoring equipment on the market.

We offer a great work environment on the High Tech Campus in Eindhoven. If you are interested more information are available at https://www.profitap.com/careers/
